{"tid":2254094,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《The Boys》監製批評《復仇者聯盟4》女英雄集結：愚蠢且是刻意人為的","createTime":"2020-10-22T14:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T17:48:23.000Z","uid":41343,"like":130,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7e79367267953303894fb60b9f320bd28b425e","tid":2254094,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/avengers-endgame-women-1563365565.jpg?resize=480:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Favengers-endgame-women-1563365565.jpg%3Fresize%3D480%3A%2A&h=b1cb55fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《黑袍糾察隊》節目統籌Eric Kripke最近談到了第二季與《復仇者聯盟：終局之戰》女<br />\n英雄集結場景的比較。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKripke最近確認，對於《復仇者聯盟：終局之戰》的失望促成了《黑袍糾察隊》中的某些<br />\n靈感。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當被問及該場景的相關問題時，她說：「這很大部份是來自於我們的執行製片人Rebecca Sonnenshine，在《復仇者聯盟：終局之戰》上映首週末的時候。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「她只是感到生氣。我也看到了！我當時想：『那是非常愚蠢，而且是相當刻意人為的。』而她的反應就像是：『大事不妙！別叫我開始做這件事。』她認為這是相當高傲的，而我也同意。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「所以這為我們創造了一個目標，一個諷刺性的目標。當超級英雄、名人或好萊塢文化中有這些荒唐可笑的事情時，我們也將立即跟上這個潮流。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/a34413368/the-boys-season-2-finale-avengers-endgame-comparison/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitalspy.com%2Ftv%2Fustv%2Fa34413368%2Fthe-boys-season-2-finale-avengers-endgame-comparison%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=28b0c7f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/a34413368/the-boys-season-2-finale-avengers-endgame-comparison/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/movie/M.1603352078.A.86F.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fmovie%2FM.1603352078.A.86F.html&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=beef1278\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/movie/M.1603352078.A.86F.html</a>"},{"pid":"96a4f7b31165a4d0f7457872f804b81f3048bd6d","tid":2254094,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":80,"score":-76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"刻意安排係冇問題<br />\n呢d係gimmick位黎<br />\n<br />\n重點係拍得好唔好睇"},{"pid":"c6bb0e5f96d30025bfdcc35552863745d0774339","tid":2254094,"uid":276676,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:30:08.000Z","msg":"呢幕仲要女蟻俠本身同蟻俠搞緊部貨VAN<br />\n都要飛返黎演野 第1次睇唔覺 睇多一兩次就覺得好嘔心<br />\n好似話比我地聽:世界末日唔緊要 最緊要我地D女人有得出位"},{"pid":"4ba55d0c700263b82a36d74b9b8e4ed14165ad06","tid":2254094,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"呢段好似係captain marvel 臨場提議加"},{"pid":"b9f84ecdc5a2de8c9c682b854842b901c0aea0fd","tid":2254094,"uid":32150,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"4ba55d0c700263b82a36d74b9b8e4ed14165ad06","tid":2254094,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"呢段好似係captain marvel 臨場提議加"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496ed556a0f90f6de9c65d9074f94b9d68fa1892","tid":2254094,"uid":35639,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:55:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">girls get it done!</span>"},{"pid":"2fa83769c60e59dc729524ece41febacf3c9eb32","tid":2254094,"uid":236794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4ba55d0c700263b82a36d74b9b8e4ed14165ad06","tid":2254094,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"呢段好似係captain marvel 臨場提議加"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T19:06:55.000Z","msg":"唔撚係嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40c933d91cce908d7342bf27138edab76e5c67b","tid":2254094,"uid":20532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"真心突兀 咁刻意反而令人反感 嘔心<img src=\"/asse